<subSubSection pageId="213" pageNumber="975" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="213.[119,1329,865,2279]" pageId="213" pageNumber="975">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[121,479,1971,2004]" pageId="213" pageNumber="975">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Vulnerable on The IUCN Red List. Mandelli’s 
<taxonomicName authority="Kaup, 1829" box="[121,211,2010,2043]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="213" pageNumber="975" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
occurs in less than 
<quantity box="[490,609,2010,2043]" metricMagnitude="6" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="213" pageNumber="975" unit="km" value="2000.0">2000 km</quantity>
?, with all known individuals at fewer than ten locations. Extent and quality ofits habitat continues to decline.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
